Description: Provides a programmatic interface to download, load, and manage
    microdata from Mexico's National Survey of Occupation and Employment
    (Encuesta Nacional de Ocupación y Empleo, ENOE), published by INEGI.
    The package supports all survey editions from 2005 onwards — including
    ENOE-N (2020 Q3–2022 Q4) — and all five questionnaire modules:
    SDEM (socio-demographic), COE1T (occupation module 1), COE2T (occupation
    module 2), HOG (household), and VIV (dwelling).  Helper functions
    facilitate multi-period panel assembly and table stacking for use in
    labour-market research, wage-gap decomposition, and related analyses.
